p.d: Cage Fury Fighting Championships, America’s top regional MMA promotion, once again returns to live action on FightBox HD on Saturday May 21st (Sunday morning May 22nd CET) for CFFC 58. Catch all the best live MMA action from the Borgata Hotel, Casino and Spa in Atlantic City, New Jersey, USA. Don’t miss this incredible mixed martial arts show from one of the biggest platforms for MMA fighters who later make it big in the UFC.
